You're doing, just... WAY more work than you need to.  Here:

[quote=&quot;clockworkdragon&quot;:3f8bysim]game.party_members = NewObjectList()
list add (game.party_members, Bob)
[color=#FF0000:3f8bysim]list add (game.party_members, Jill)[/color:3f8bysim]
